FBIS3-51375 "drlat012_k_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 SOUTH AMERICA Argentina Former Chamber of Deputies' President Pugliese Dies PY1801174694 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 1256 GMT 17 Jan 94 PY1801174694 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Tandil, 17 Jan (NA) -- Juan Carlos Pugliese, a former Chamber of Deputies president, died today at 0900 in Tandil, his home town, where he lived since giving up public functions. Pugliese was admitted to a local hospital by mid-week last week. He was the president of the Chamber of Deputies from the reestablishment of democracy in 1983 to 1989 when he left to become economy minister during the final stretch of the Raul Alfonsin administration.
